919951442.text: "Indeed, overexpression of CARMA1 enhances PMA- and Bcl10 dependent NF-kappaB activation that is blocked by expression of CARMA1 lacking the Bcl10 interacting domain, demonstrating that CARMA1 acts upstream of Bcl10."
